# HNU Official Website - Makefile Quick Reference

## 🚀 Quick Start Commands

```bash
make help          # Show this help message
make install       # Install dependencies
make dev           # Start development server
make build         # Build the application
make deploy        # Deploy to current branch
```

## 📋 Available Targets

### Development
- `make install` - Install dependencies
- `make dev` - Start development server
- `make start` - Start production server

### Building
- `make build` - Build the application
- `make build-clean` - Clean build and rebuild

### Code Quality
- `make format` - Format code with Prettier
- `make format-check` - Check code formatting
- `make lint` - Run ESLint
- `make lint-fix` - Fix ESLint issues
- `make type-check` - Run TypeScript type checking
- `make qa` - Run all quality checks

### Deployment
- `make deploy` - Deploy to current branch
- `make deploy-prod` - Deploy to production (main branch)
- `make deploy-staging` - Deploy to staging (develop branch)
- `make deploy-ts` - Deploy using TypeScript script
- `make deploy-full` - Full deployment pipeline

### Git Operations
- `make status` - Show git status
- `make pull` - Pull latest changes
- `make push` - Push changes to remote

### Utilities
- `make clean` - Clean build artifacts
- `make check-node` - Check Node.js version
- `make check-deps` - Check dependency status
- `make update-deps` - Update dependencies

## 🔧 Advanced Usage

### Full Production Deployment
```bash
make deploy-prod-full
```

### Full Staging Deployment
```bash
make deploy-staging-full
```

### Quality Assurance + Build
```bash
make qa build
```

### Clean and Rebuild
```bash
make clean install build
```

